Universal Electronics (http://www.ueic.com/~ueic/) has a wide range
of universal Remote Control Units (that can be programmed to emulate
other Remote Control Units).  Check out
http://207.126.118.58/~ueic/eu/ofazapperline.html for several small
ones.

